bug.short_desc: Submitting task fails with invalid date / time format error

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 86458 eclipse log file containing error details
Mylyn 2.2.0I20071220-1700
When submitting an updated task (user reassigned) an error box appears "Submit error" with the following text:
"Invalid date / time format. Expected dd/MMM/yy hh:mm aInvalid date / time format. Expected dd/MMM/yy hh:mm a"
According to .log file the problem is JIRA sending an invalid date / time format in the "Start Event" field.
*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of bug 213397 ***
